An '''ST box''' was a device which, when attached to the [[Sublight engine/Legends|sublight drives]] of a ship, could mask its [[Transponder code/Legends|transponder code]] with that of another ship. The use of ST boxes was considered standard operating procedure by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] member [[Deen Voorson]], and was described in ''[[Cracken's Rebel Field Guide]]''.<ref name="Slaying">{{JournalCite|9|Slaying Dragons}}</ref>

